; Box — grid (3, 4) → world (6, 0.5, 8)
; Initial top face = NORMAL_A.
; After push RIGHT → top = IMPACT_A (defeats normal enemy).
; After push UP   → top = HEAVY   (defeats normal enemy).
; After push DOWN → top = ENERGY  (DENIED — teaches player to read the face).
